        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You favor bows and other elegant weapons. You gain access to all uncommon weapons with the elf trait. You have familiarity with weapons with the elf trait plus @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Longbow]{Longbows}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Composite Longbow]{Composite Longbows}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Rapier]{Rapiers}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Shortbow]{Shortbows}, and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-srd.Item.Composite Shortbow]{Composite Shortbows}â€”for the purposes of proficiency, you treat any of these that are martial weapons as simple weapons and any that are advanced weapons as martial weapons.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, whenever you get a critical hit with one of these weapons, you get its critical specialization effect.</p>"
